description: Every night can be Mexican night with these easy chicken tortillas. A fast and simple crowd-pleaser.
keywords: Tortilla,Low saturated fat,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,Microwave,High protein,High fibre,Leftover chicken,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Easy Crispy Chicken Tortillas Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 10 pack Old El Paso regular flour tortillas
35g Old El Paso crispy chicken spice mix for soft tacos
500g RSPCA approved chicken breast fillets (thinly sliced)

recipeInstructions.text: Place chicken in a large bowl, add spice mix and toss to coat well.
Heat olive oil in a large frying pan over high heat. Add chicken and corn, then cook for 10-12 minutes, stirring occasionally, until corn is slightly charred and chicken is golden brown.
Remove freshness sachet from the tortilla packet and microwave on high for 25 seconds or until warmed.
Fill tortillas with chicken and corn to serve.
